<hr local-id=3D"41fef660-526a-4a8d-a7ec-dab6c88133a7">
<h3 local-id=3D"d24b7949-b026-4855-9375-ea1811a53220" id=3D"CourseOperation=
s-8.8.2AddParticipanttoCoursewithImportFile">8.8.2 Add Participant to Cours=
e with Import File</h3>
<p local-id=3D"4b22d1c2-00b2-47bc-bd93-ffc4cf242964"><strong>User Story:</s=
trong> <br>
AS an Admin channel <br>
I WANT to import participants to course <br>
SO THAT I can import new participant or add re-exam participants to the cou=
rse</p>
<p local-id=3D"751c4752-a3f6-475e-95eb-f3a742119faa"><strong>Acceptance Cri=
teria:</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"08aa973a-7fc6-4291-8a84-c43a6e3efcb5"><strong>A. Add Normal =
Participant to Course with Import File</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"3456ccb4-7666-4ca4-90b9-935b1d3e8ce7">Importing rules based =
on course type and channel:</p>
<p local-id=3D"3924d5d8-b3ae-4657-861b-b48acf90f69f"><strong>SHINE Course (=
Banca Channel Only):</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"51265300-7607-43bf-9655-c2bc16c13bd2">
<li local-id=3D"9a290b34-3621-4aa0-90a8-f82d26d016f7">
<p local-id=3D"917803a0-6812-4fff-8608-28f494474d0b">Import action means: <=
strong>CREATE new participant</strong> and add the created participant to S=
HINE course</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9c529f2e-8099-4cb6-b184-0676a5521507">
<p local-id=3D"0da5e070-4b04-4836-bd21-48f93e071303">Import only if partici=
pant <strong>doesn't exist</strong> =E2=86=92 Create new participant + Add =
to course + Normal exam</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a3c72c9d-02cf-4816-b19e-d78728c4d8e0">
<p local-id=3D"03e10500-f5d8-4efb-8d3d-6ab37ba9eec0">Reject if participant =
<strong>already exists</strong> =E2=86=92 Return to failed list</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0cf20555-ea34-42e7-8e64-3cf5c453b58d">
<p local-id=3D"39e80862-dd31-447c-9d19-e82a8b1bf4ad"><strong>Business Reaso=
n:</strong> SHINE is the <strong>first course</strong> - participants shoul=
dn't pre-exist. If they do exist, use "Add Participant" function instead of=
 import.</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"517347f3-72e1-47ab-bd54-0d21effae5d9"><strong>After-SHINE Co=
urse (All Channels):</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"b55b5bcd-1ddd-49e4-85dd-8a1fca389dca">
<li local-id=3D"e02ea8b0-5e3e-4539-98a0-9bc35321c25b">
<p local-id=3D"56abb339-67c0-42d0-9006-115de9b693da">Import action means: <=
strong>ADD existing participant</strong> to course (no creation)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"59f411d6-8700-4fad-b66c-67d27a2979b6">
<p local-id=3D"818245ed-4326-4bf7-aeef-a5f6eeebe3c4">Participant exists =E2=
=86=92 Add existing participant to course + Normal exam</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"faa376e8-8628-4d89-8e71-18c816473cfa">
<p local-id=3D"880c63fd-8bda-4bfe-9fe5-cfefff8cc7a0">Reject if participant =
<strong>doesn't exist</strong> =E2=86=92 Return to failed list</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3df52049-6cef-4d1f-a710-5abc84295a41">
<p local-id=3D"d5b6f573-e45e-47d4-ace9-2b3d97801a1b"><strong>Business Reaso=
n:</strong> After-SHINE happens <strong>after SHINE completion</strong> - p=
articipants must already exist in system. Import function only adds existin=
g participants to course, not creating new ones.</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"82eb3663-bbb9-4a60-83ae-aa8851f1e893"><strong>B. Add Re-Exam=
 Participant to Course with Import File</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"f0125fac-342a-4edc-b8ed-66ea5e2dfcd3"><strong>Business Use C=
ase:</strong><br>
When Participant Failed the SHINE course, we allow them to re-take the SHIN=
E course with the add existing Participant to SHINE course with importing f=
eature.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"b8d50e8d-7b37-410a-9427-376dca6b5786">
<li local-id=3D"79258a16-784a-45e6-895d-cf9fb093c0c2">
<p local-id=3D"e329e13d-4cbf-4f3a-bbd8-ad6c7084db19"><strong>CONDITION:</st=
rong> Participant <strong>exists</strong> in system AND all of the followin=
g are true:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"f5782dcc-1b47-4fd6-949c-be8ada010121">
<li local-id=3D"d994cdcf-24ee-4076-87e8-fbb23851c2b3">
<p local-id=3D"a048a5bd-9a55-489d-bc08-89cb56336ae9">AOL exams passed</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"cb57c54f-fbce-4784-bd65-a4ef2aa8deb5">
<p local-id=3D"11db4de6-ac5b-45ff-b086-3207e78556ab">Attendance completed</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0bf7a407-4249-442d-a691-e1e6f214a3eb">
<p local-id=3D"09f95cb3-33cc-4e8b-b753-e859ada0c9a1">Course completed withi=
n past 45 days</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2f032910-0dc7-4f80-aab0-ed2cff1d2b81">
<p local-id=3D"47bf2694-2747-456b-ad9e-c5d8185561f9">MOF exam not passed</p=
></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"ac0d4d35-5c51-44e7-b6c4-e4059571a538">
<p local-id=3D"158f4c57-09d4-498c-87da-44d713cec947"><strong>ACTION:</stron=
g> ADD existing participant to course with exam type set as "Re MOF Examina=
tion"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3cf6d6b6-8de8-4d42-bd05-ebb3f0796c58">
<p local-id=3D"9e749c38-85ff-43bd-a7a6-f597045b2bf5">If CONDITION is not me=
t: Return to failed list</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dd8ce63a-cbf2-4098-a7e9-7ea5c39d6219">
<p local-id=3D"fa8eaf5c-96ee-4568-ab67-57c172f831ec"><strong>Business Reaso=
n:</strong> Re-exam eligibility ensures participant completed all requireme=
nts except MOF within valid timeframe.</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"d50c8ada-2809-434e-9176-b235d5b2c8f6"><strong>Import File Fo=
rmat:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"e3=
69832d-b263-4404-adb1-d792cef23a67" class=3D"confluenceTable">
