<p local-id=3D"ce6605f8-86ed-4329-87b6-5d002e2507f9"><strong>Import Process=
:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"0f59511b-66e4-4c1e-bfb6-b0f19064ba48">
<li local-id=3D"a894d7b7-e369-4635-8b15-913ae8251cb0">
<p local-id=3D"a7d932b1-2364-455f-865e-8f787688ed40">User uploads import fi=
le</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f1061341-eb4f-42dd-a03f-7be5864f180d">
<p local-id=3D"5723cf49-6676-45a6-9c91-68a17b563b6c">System validates file =
format</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d30627e2-14d1-42b9-a9c9-96cc5d8f0c92">
<p local-id=3D"ce60f04d-2bc0-45dc-9f09-3c979a467e4b">System processes each =
row:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"34df2146-bde4-45a5-8ba4-7341cb33cf0d">
<li local-id=3D"9e1d0515-522c-4336-8d97-5f9cd9a3f28d">
<p local-id=3D"05c14a7a-c32f-42c7-aa02-ff703d1f5f47">Validates participant =
data</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"de12d08d-774f-4086-8488-bdfa85b122a8">
<p local-id=3D"127967c9-39df-4e01-b0a5-2b998e3ec7f0">Checks existence (for =
After-SHINE) or non-existence (for SHINE)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"158a43e7-80d3-4d03-902b-ae45410d5a9e">
<p local-id=3D"1c3cd873-a7b4-474e-9a06-d054edb14220">Validates re-exam cond=
itions (if applicable)</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"de43fc34-fda6-47e6-acc6-c3e5658bbd53">
<p local-id=3D"b7e7703d-70dc-4775-9c65-601501b2c87c">System creates/adds pa=
rticipants based on course type and channel rules</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"339fc271-b8ff-4b2d-bb61-624b450a3239">
