<h3 local-id=3D"907e3ede-d34f-43a4-8a2e-c3582bbd1235" id=3D"CourseOperation=
s-8.8.7ConfirmPassedParticipant">8.8.7 Confirm Passed Participant</h3>
<p local-id=3D"3da6d6a9-eb32-4f07-b887-21bb176fde2a"><strong>User Story:</s=
trong> <br>
AS an admin <br>
I NEED to confirm passed participants <br>
SO THAT I can finalize participant completion status and trigger certificat=
ion processes</p>
<p local-id=3D"16ff4c51-d6ec-4214-9ae6-156026dd2e5c"><strong>Process:</stro=
ng></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"4b186e09-d857-405f-a0bf-63d0096c360b">
<li local-id=3D"ba719b4a-2c7b-4d9c-94a8-82430740d1e8">
<p local-id=3D"f52823ab-00e6-430f-a253-e5536972a03a"><strong>LMS Event:</st=
rong> Reminder at Course End date + 1 day</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"609ae6fc-2fa1-4e42-a258-a0fa8862eaed">
<p local-id=3D"32fe4425-5077-4053-8008-0b4aa7f22fe8"><strong>Email sent to:=
</strong> AA_admin (SHINE) or channel email (After-shine)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b461ea9d-f049-4817-a78b-c3604573af70">
<p local-id=3D"d05a7f7b-e090-469e-9344-2ad19c00df96"><strong>Admin action:<=
/strong> Login to LMS and confirm passed participants</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"03017a10-84f2-423b-a55a-8844993a7a6d">
<p local-id=3D"cdfeb896-084f-4521-a2a0-c6209dc2dce8"><strong>System check:<=
/strong> Verify attachment uploaded (SHINE only)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8b621a10-d5a9-4ac6-a1bb-bb9df3c899cf">
<p local-id=3D"c9ad00d9-db6b-4978-acb7-51d6d4a43e25"><strong>Email confirma=
tion sent</strong> to appropriate admin</p></li>
</ol>
