<hr local-id=3D"415e7907-f6c3-46bb-abae-9b4025dab3bd">
<h3 local-id=3D"b8d29a0b-2dcc-4123-b318-9c15c2ba5041" id=3D"CourseOperation=
s-8.8.11RuleforCalculateFinalResult">8.8.11 Rule for Calculate Final Result=
</h3>
<p local-id=3D"da104aa9-5935-4bb6-85f6-6285706a08e6"><strong>User Story:</s=
trong> <br>
AS THE System <br>
I NEED to automatically calculate final result for each participant <br>
SO THAT I can determine course completion status based on defined criteria<=
/p>
<p local-id=3D"537ba26c-db3d-4fe1-ac07-f9ac5427e0f6"><strong>Acceptance Cri=
teria:</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"29f0e31b-232e-4718-9006-1fabaa63efdf">LMS returns final resu=
lt based on course type and completion criteria.</p>
<p local-id=3D"19370b1e-b146-4095-bd09-61b558916be8"><strong>Course Type SH=
INE:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"f9981d5d-3f88-41da-82b9-2d59a3f4570a">
<li local-id=3D"e03a07fe-627a-4f87-ad35-8544da96cf48">
<p local-id=3D"416995bb-2e63-49be-9b5a-4beaddb2f4f4">Attendance: Full</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"de6d413b-2d89-4589-b589-f5e33cbe3ded">
<p local-id=3D"5883810c-c10c-40c6-b894-8560e19ab483">AOL: Passed</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"00afa768-c802-4cf1-a783-a3153eb35196">
<p local-id=3D"f88eaaa8-9068-4401-8e7e-996ff56562a8">MOF &gt;=3D 30</p></li=
>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"11059623-03f5-41ab-a9b4-fa6979a599a7"><strong>Course Type Pr=
oduct:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"f2e0df43-99b5-44e1-8589-a090f6e8deb2">
<li local-id=3D"5725a35f-cd3f-4801-be8d-e1fe2dc9aa56">
<p local-id=3D"7afa29a6-5d5c-4bc2-a318-05c409766eee">Attendance: Full</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"b738bf9a-b939-4ff3-b66b-c8dd6e8f3473">
<p local-id=3D"bf89c8b1-2124-48c4-8a55-79c23c362b2c">AOL: Passed</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"1b3e1f29-4be8-484b-b5d3-81ef9c11366b"><strong>Course Type Sk=
ill:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"37eee09b-68fc-4323-b51c-15a7a24ef435">
<li local-id=3D"bea13233-e754-48b3-ade8-709d2a8a635b">
<p local-id=3D"12fbaf5f-96ec-401c-8449-b080835b3a9c">Attendance: Full</p></=
li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"44af0566-00f6-482e-a44c-b4dce50db3e6"><strong>Calculation Lo=
gic:</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"be95c404-dda6-4ba4-80c2-dc070e630c8c"><strong>SHINE Course:<=
/strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">IF (Att=
endance =3D Full) AND (All AOL Exams =3D Passed) AND (MOF Score &gt;=3D 30)
THEN
    Final Result =3D Passed
ELSE
    Final Result =3D Failed
END IF</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"3e68938a-f28d-4bce-a8da-1d149fe97f60"><strong>Product Course=
:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">IF (Att=
endance =3D Full) AND (All AOL Exams =3D Passed)
THEN
    Final Result =3D Passed
ELSE
    Final Result =3D Failed
END IF</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"6cb79018-80b6-4621-a433-32ac64b7224c"><strong>Skill Course:<=
/strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">IF (Att=
endance =3D Full)
THEN
    Final Result =3D Passed
ELSE
    Final Result =3D Failed
END IF</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"99caa816-8979-42a5-886b-fa2113524cd4"><strong>Automatic Calc=
ulation:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"0e079032-883a-4d88-bf41-f1b91e93aa92">
<li local-id=3D"02c445d8-1051-4900-bd5e-3af4a1cf90c3">
<p local-id=3D"175b9bb9-e39c-40bf-a8a1-586b001bdd09">System calculates fina=
l result automatically when:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"5825adba-aaa0-4b0c-826b-e7b6d606e112">
<li local-id=3D"1e0ae7d6-5e41-4e21-8a7a-727a4813cf6b">
<p local-id=3D"58e233bd-c55b-425a-861d-c544fe32b107">Attendance data is upd=
ated</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"67bcfa01-91ac-4870-b855-12f36e27b9c8">
<p local-id=3D"4cf6b6f9-31cf-43fe-a1ad-3da4c5a0f998">AOL exam results are u=
pdated</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ac3121ec-5725-453c-af83-5eff10395e18">
<p local-id=3D"8e6a529c-d51d-4e12-b999-0865fa48598d">MOF exam results are i=
mported</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"b96c64bb-bc55-46c7-8eef-c3b0610584ad">
<p local-id=3D"26055b9b-efce-4370-9d0d-d0d66f787377">Final result updates i=
n real-time as data changes</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"71e03427-84f2-4b87-9e6b-b87af877397c">
<p local-id=3D"9aebc35f-0d75-44af-bef8-83b663807014">Final result cannot be=
 manually set (use Section 8.8.12 for manual override)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"237f9b8f-4bdb-496b-a194-ec60f7303453"><strong>Business Rules=
:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"8e90c906-a8d6-4b45-899f-002d6d3be42c">
<li local-id=3D"ff4ed4ec-e1fa-46b8-bffb-7b47ed6e86c3">
<p local-id=3D"78391f44-fde8-4bea-b5e2-a2549482f384">All criteria must be m=
et for Final Result =3D Passed</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4b2b621e-8b5b-4373-b93e-f00958ba8457">
<p local-id=3D"8a60617d-99d3-49e6-9543-f8b0b9151d55">If any criterion is no=
t met, Final Result =3D Failed</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fd968fa1-6335-48e0-b01d-43330e929ee0">
<p local-id=3D"b64b2a70-6767-4fab-800c-303d72f031f5">Final result calculati=
on is automatic and cannot be disabled</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9e369638-d3f0-47a1-9792-18de8121537e">
<p local-id=3D"8e562751-692e-4a46-8056-4bae324d7eef">Manual override availa=
ble for special cases (Section 8.8.12)</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"c3fb75f8-83b1-4637-911a-fa7c29f15353">
<h3 local-id=3D"b6100693-0f40-4881-a122-7443b19e2167" id=3D"CourseOperation=
s-8.8.12ManuallySetPassed/Failed">8.8.12 Manually Set Passed/Failed</h3>
<p local-id=3D"4b7b0f1f-1ca6-4317-9975-4fcd18d145f9"><strong>User Story:</s=
trong> <br>
AS an Admin or Head <br>
I NEED to manually set final result for participants <br>
SO THAT I can handle special cases and exceptions</p>
<p local-id=3D"48883ad7-0b31-40fa-8104-846fe1b91617"><strong>Acceptance Cri=
teria:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"93158e6c-5d20-4226-97cb-a05e05d5a190">
<li local-id=3D"4d93cc28-dd94-4ef2-985c-ae10f1bb10c6">
<p local-id=3D"19afe68f-3c31-43a2-99f5-0ea469a1ae18">Function only for Admi=
n or Head</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"68341a85-34fc-48ca-aae9-cac7d2880424">
<p local-id=3D"07144dab-902e-4abf-b6e1-9b3d8f9c3451">Button to set final re=
sult</p></li>
