<p local-id=3D"ad167ea0-1ef4-4325-b457-bcaa73c7abf8">Value recorded as: pas=
sed** or failed**</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"654ae6b4-4b44-4d35-bef1-f32d66a2aec3">
<p local-id=3D"c50733cd-a9e2-4ee7-863b-a32ac154e6b0">Attachment recorded in=
 participant list</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"c09d657d-b97f-4cd6-814c-d64f43ea6c81"><strong>Manual Overrid=
e Process:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"4d7639d8-63dc-42d8-a914-a9a2893ddde9">
<li local-id=3D"18f5df74-fadc-4e61-ad54-9530349db24f">
<p local-id=3D"e683e674-0463-4a29-a8a8-0ec5e10b9fa5">Admin/Head selects par=
ticipant(s) from list</p></li>
