<p local-id=3D"e3398880-d8e7-4c18-a8bf-cdde8de8b32b">Admin/Head selects res=
ult: Passed** or Failed**</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"28012c89-c38d-4dc7-a805-3c29b5047f02">
<p local-id=3D"681705e9-c214-49d2-ad03-b96d03b08f2b">Admin/Head enters reas=
on (mandatory)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e3002e3f-1f4d-4f83-9cb5-ee98b0b97b3e">
<p local-id=3D"98acf730-4613-4ee1-bf24-5c8516dbb3a2">Admin/Head uploads att=
achment (optional but recommended)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ad29a8ab-43e0-42d6-a080-30a3e851a392">
<p local-id=3D"d194487a-9467-4556-bc0f-68901ac20bcf">Admin/Head confirms ac=
tion</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bc5ba409-72eb-4aef-b41f-e50af09fcdec">
<p local-id=3D"7e1f6f1f-6eb4-4158-bee6-a9c0e0d1e6f2">System updates final r=
esult with ** indicator</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"16056726-0aaf-454e-b536-5fe781d2c926">
<p local-id=3D"121db969-f590-435a-ab81-5355ae48f86c">System records reason =
and attachment</p></li>
