<p local-id=3D"96583be5-693a-4021-87a2-3d1eb4a752d0"><strong>Business Rules=
:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"2aa9f8ae-e937-4f35-b67d-692428857446">
<li local-id=3D"25c16210-8d36-40a8-9db8-22987ffe0423">
<p local-id=3D"b6635eb3-1811-4213-a773-e4986929ea75">Only Admin and Head Ch=
annel can perform manual override</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6f820126-2916-4bc5-822e-2042c9d21d92">
<p local-id=3D"dec127bf-daa0-4f9d-9a5d-18e0423d8366">Manual override create=
s ** indicator in final result</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"201815e2-fd42-4def-81bb-87b6056a1360">
<p local-id=3D"a30a19ae-718d-4755-959a-09736c5ffede">Reason is mandatory fo=
r audit purposes</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4c8e5c11-0fbf-4b49-bfdb-f93b4a52fd9c">
<p local-id=3D"85e92c58-b115-4856-b74f-011d38be815e">Attachment is recommen=
ded for documentation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fcc615cd-f762-4234-8505-4b21122c5d88">
<p local-id=3D"c0ef895f-c116-4622-b616-b2412c3edccc">Manual override cannot=
 be reversed (audit trail)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"65d8488c-af26-4132-8b53-c16060d53682">
<p local-id=3D"317a3d99-8d90-4212-a7b4-3a0a360553bd">Manual override takes =
precedence over automatic calculation</p></li>
</ol>
