<p local-id=3D"7dbf1a8b-ca6e-4834-a7c9-0480c7fd9dee"><strong>Business Rules=
:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"ca64f549-f952-46f9-9ba8-4a0d42407d42">
<li local-id=3D"4e681262-cc1f-4d41-8d11-74fc4d420c29">
<p local-id=3D"a8c95be4-21b0-47f6-8a23-14f71d3bcb97">Agent codes granted vi=
a external API only</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"557d50a2-479b-4c2b-b739-29a4803b7d66">
<p local-id=3D"614af241-bd11-4fe2-bed3-4cd1103d2ba4">Agent codes typically =
granted after participant confirmation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"45593fef-2df1-4b7c-acd8-9a7d926551d0">
<p local-id=3D"248c6080-03c6-4b09-8b70-e9e2bc8c1bb9">Agent code cannot be m=
anually edited</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9482077c-f44d-42ad-8a22-76adda24f9ff">
<p local-id=3D"611ef9d2-b188-49d9-bb50-2a842f7e23c4">Agent code displayed o=
nce granted</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cb1f84b0-a888-4a8c-a6dc-d40f8e096e85">
<p local-id=3D"fbf1bbc0-adf5-41e6-9317-3628f751f645">Agent code is unique p=
er participant</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"ff6a4e54-d1bd-4145-b896-f62dc1b801fe"><strong>Course Type Re=
strictions:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"133edf4d-ddeb-48d3-abc1-eea889a19607">
<li local-id=3D"86b9201d-7fd5-4d7f-906f-b00e0e015481">
<p local-id=3D"b5825fd9-addc-46f9-8801-ad3674559786"><strong>SHINE Courses:=
</strong> Agent code required for passed participants</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fe93aa26-eebc-41f2-a857-7f4039f6a5bc">
<p local-id=3D"ea9335d7-1959-45f6-8085-545703cc2f19"><strong>Product Course=
s:</strong> Agent code optional</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"56bb37ea-13bd-4734-a37f-574da620701e">
<p local-id=3D"121a2971-1418-40fb-8070-4a6fc7a2f7a1"><strong>Skill Courses:=
</strong> Agent code not applicable</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"a54ede6a-4bf5-44af-8d83-125cc1da10f7"><strong>Authorization:=
</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"9d225fbc-1ebc-459a-8473-9df8fb948dcf">
<li local-id=3D"92685170-3e97-4d1f-bb93-f8f681e3c698">
<p local-id=3D"1d22b242-9f7e-49a8-9c91-18dc432c04ef">Agent code granting is=
 handled by external system</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4e2aa526-4cf1-4784-8857-f571a9e139bc">
<p local-id=3D"8b230a8d-614d-4fd3-8dac-c77332d4cb5d">LMS displays agent cod=
e once received via API</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5f0cf900-9ddc-42bc-a77c-0938e322a42b">
<p local-id=3D"6eb0c1cc-5d2f-4c16-a3bd-ffd91453e66d">No manual agent code a=
ssignment in LMS</p></li>
</ul>
